<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٩٦٤ - ق د س]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تقدَّسَ يتقدَّس، تقدُّسًا، فهو مُتَقدِّس<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تقدَّس الرَّجلُ:</span> تطهَّر.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تقدَّس اللهُ:</span> تنزَّه <span class="c1">"جلّ جلاله وتقدّست أسماؤُه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>